# Professional CV Template By Deepak Deshkar

A modern, responsive, and ATS-friendly CV/resume template built with HTML, Tailwind CSS, and enhanced with professional typography. Features one-click PDF export functionality.

## ğŸš€ Features

- **ATS-Optimized Structure**: Carefully formatted for Applicant Tracking Systems
- **Responsive Design**: Perfect viewing on all devices
- **One-Click PDF Export**: Easy download with html2pdf.js
- **Professional Typography**: Using Inter & Lato fonts for optimal readability
- **Print-Friendly**: Optimized for both digital viewing and printing
- **Customizable**: Easy to modify sections and styling

